body:
Closes https://github.com/gofractally/psibase/issues/328

The query
```
query {
    getFractals(user: "alice")
    {
        edges {
            node {
                key {
                    fractal
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

Will return, for example
```
{
    "data": {
        "getFractals": {
            "edges": [
                {
                    "node": {
                        "key": {
                            "fractal": "astronauts"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    }
}
```
